Auto-update — publish/update via Chrome Web Store and optionally provide enterprise/private deployment instructions.

23) UX polish & helpers 

Presets — Balanced, Fast, Thorough, Max-Compatible with brief descriptions.

One-click common actions — "Download all images", "Download visible images", "Download originals".

Quickstart wizard — onboarding that walks through selecting a site, picking a selector, and running a sample.

Snapshot / debug export — export debug package (screenshot, HTML snippet, logs) to attach to bug reports.

